    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"18\">Category: Clan</strong><br data-start=\"18\" data-end=\"21\" /><strong data-start=\"21\" data-end=\"63\" data-is-only-node>Prerequisite: Ōtsutsuki Clan, Level 4+</strong></p><p data-start=\"67\" data-end=\"189\">You have trained your Byakugan to advance its potency, enhancing its visual prowess and unlocking more of its potential.</p><ul data-start=\"191\" data-end=\"609\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node><li data-start=\"191\" data-end=\"253\">Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"412\">While your Byakugan is active, you may use your Intelligence instead of Wisdom for any Wisdom-based ability checks or saving throws you are proficient in.</li><li data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"609\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node>Your Byakugan gains one of the following features from the Hyuga clan: Combat Insight, Immense Distance, Penetrative Vision, Perceptive Insight, Perceptive Predictions, or Perceptive Resilience.</li></ul>",
